enchantlib.midnightconfig.title: Better Chiseled Bookshelf Config
enchantlib.midnightconfig.modifyRedstone: If enable, the redstone output will be in pair with the amount of books in the shelf.
enchantlib.midnightconfig.normalBookPowe: How much power each book should give
enchantlib.midnightconfig.enchantedBookP: How much power each enchanted book should give
enchantlib.midnightconfig.particleChance: Bigger values means less frequent particles
enchantlib.midnightconfig.tableSize.tool: The area in which the table will search for bookshelves
enchantlib.midnightconfig.allowList.tool: Blocks in this list will be ignored and will not block enchantment power.
enchantlib.midnightconfig.denyList.toolt: Blocks in this list will cause enchantment power to be blocked
enchantlib.midnightconfig.obType.tooltip: Determines what type of blocks will block the shelf power
enchantlib.midnightconfig.XZSize.tooltip: Determines how much to each side the table should search for shelves
enchantlib.midnightconfig.YSize.tooltip: Determines how high up the table should search for shelves
enchantlib.midnightconfig.yGoesDown.tool:
If enable, the table will get shelves belows its Y coordinate.
Same value as Shelf Height
enchantlib.midnightconfig.getMoreShelves: If enable, the table will get shelves that are behind other shelves
enchantlib.midnightconfig.disableLogging: Disables the performance warning for tables bigger than 15+
enchantlib.midnightconfig.multiplyNormal: Multiply Normal Book Power For Enchanted Book
If the enchanted book power should be the normal book but multiplied by some value
